                            <comment id="14380044" author="rohini" created="Wed, 25 Mar 2015 15:29:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;  This is a special case where multiple LocalRearrange in POSplit point to same vertex group. We usually avoid keeping them in POSplit, but the LocalRearranges are in different nested splits. Not changing MultiQueryOptimizer to avoid this as well as vertex group handles multiple edges from same vertex unlike regular edge.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
